---
// Trust & Clinical Evidence
---

<section id="trust" class="section trust">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="trust-content reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="trust-accent-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <h2 class="trust-title">学术与临床<br />双重背书</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="trust-narrative reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="trust-body">
        <p>获得 <strong class="trust-em">1,000+</strong> 公立医院皮肤科临床选用，<strong class="trust-em">3,000+</strong> 皮肤科及儿科医生共同推荐，至今已成为 <strong class="trust-em">200万+</strong> 敏感肌家庭的信赖之选。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="trust-publications reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="trust-pub">
        <span class="trust-pub-source">中华皮肤科杂志 · 2022</span>
        <p class="trust-pub-detail">北京友谊医院双盲对照研究证实：止痒效果等同于弱效激素，止痒速度优于弱效激素。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-pub">
        <span class="trust-pub-source">SCI · IJMS · 2022</span>
        <p class="trust-pub-detail">四川大学华西医院研究证明：海得宝能提高激素有效率高达 6 倍。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-pub">
        <span class="trust-pub-source">中山大学第五医院</span>
        <p class="trust-pub-detail">临床治疗特应性皮炎有效率 67%，止痒有效率 79%。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .trust {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding-top: var(--space-6xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-6xl);
    position: relative;
  }

  .trust::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-brand-subtle), transparent);
  }

  .trust-content {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .trust-accent-line {
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-brand);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .trust-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 200;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
  }

  /* ── Narrative intro ── */
  .trust-narrative {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .trust-body {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-soft);
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  .trust-em {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-brand-dark);
  }

  /* ── Publications ── */
  .trust-publications {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    padding-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .trust-pub-source {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-brand);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .trust-pub-detail {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-soft);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .trust-publications {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }
  }
</style>
